headline: What Recent Developments Mean For The Evolving NextEra Energy Investment Story
summary: NextEra Energy’s latest narrative update comes with a slightly higher fair value estimate of about $91.14 per share, underpinned by a stable discount rate at roughly 6.956% and a modestly stronger long term revenue growth outlook of around 11.69% fueled by structural demand for clean power and data center capacity.
